      "title": "A gas ship arrives",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A ship carrying 3700 metric tons of gas has now reached Colombo and is undergoing gas inspection, Litro Gas Company's media spokesperson V. Mr. Keteswaram said today (22).",
        "Mr. Keteswaram said that the unloading will start as soon as the inspection work is completed and he also mentioned that seven stocks of gas are to be reached within this month."
      ],
